description.narrative: This activity will design and implement an initiative to support Botswana improve delivery of practical, industry-led livestock training and extension services that will contribute to increased productivity in the beef sector. This initiative will take a capacity building approach, working through the Bostwana Ministry of Agriculture and target the communal beef sector.
